'''DTC'''

DTC is a french expression exclusivelu used by DCSchoolStylez Member. It means "Dans ton Cul". In english it would be "Up Your Ass"

You shouldn't say that to someone you do not know well...

An exemple of DTC's use : 

<HaZarD> il est ou gadi ?
